initio.title: Initio
initio.description: [Beginner] This magic is to turn on electrical devices near you. To unleash the magic hold your wand horizontally, and rotate it to perpendicular. Say the magic word.

arktisz.title: Arktisz
arktisz.description: [Beginner] This magic is to freeze your opponent. To unleash the magic hold your wand horizontally, and dont move it. Say the word lumen

lumen.title: Lumen
lumen.description: This magic is for beginners. It lets the magician to turn up and down the lights. To unleash the magic hold your wand horizontally. Have your arms half bent in front of you, to your left.  Move your hand from left to right and say the magic word lumen

komikus.title: Komikus
komikus.description: This magic makes fun of things. It is very useful when you fear of the mumus. Say ‘komikus’ and make a line in front of you which goes in 45 degrees in the air with your wand, starting from the left bottom corner

invito.title: Invito
invito.description: This magic invites pulls things to you like an invisible power. You need to start with your hands bent in front of you, then you need to straighten them while saying the word ‘invito’

abrakadabra.title: Abrakadabra
abrakadabra.description: This is a very powerful magic which causes serios damage to your opponent wizard. To achieve this magic, you should hold the magic wand in your hand and make a circle in the air, beginning from the bottom and doing it clockwise. While doing the movement you have to say the magic word: abrakadabra
